  <sect3 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Iagno</title>

    <para>
      <application>iagno</application> is a computer version of the game 
      Reversi, more popularly called Othello. Iagno is a 
      two player strategy game similar to Go. The board is 8 by 8 with 
      tiles that are black on one side and white on the other side.
    </para>

    &lfs76_checked;

